high_descs: Move forward and face the toilet to your right.
Take the soap off the top of the toilet in front of you.
Move back and face the cabinet by the toilet in front of you.
Open the cabinet, place the soap inside and close the cabinet in front of you.
Face the toilet in front of you.
Take the soap off of the top of the toilet in front of you.
Move back and face the cabinet by the toilet in front of you.
Open the cabinet, place the soap inside and close the cabinet in front of you.
anns.task_desc: Place soap in cabinet under the sink.

high_descs: Turn left for one step, turn right and over to the toilet, turn right and face the toilet.
Pick up the bar of pink soap on the right, on top of the toilet tank.
Turn around for two steps, turn right for one step, turn right again and stop.
Open the left cabinet door under the sink and put the soap on the front left, top facing left, and shut the door.
Walk toward the toilet and stop.
Pick up the pink soap on top of the toilet tank.
Turn around for one step, turn right for one step, turn right again and stop.
Open the left cabinet door under the sink and put the soap above the one already there, standing up.
anns.task_desc: Put two bars of soap in a bottom cabinet, one horizontal and one vertical.

high_descs: Go to the toilet
Grab a bar of soap from the top of the toilet
Back up from the toilet and look down
Put the soap in the left cabinet
Move forward to the toilet
Grab a bar of soap from the top of the toilet
Back up from the toilet and look down
Put the soap in the left cabinet
anns.task_desc: Putting two bars of soap in a cabinet
